{"tid":401323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"萬字送禮文：李克勤慶祝成立30週年演唱會（尾場）觀後感","createTime":"2017-09-15T13:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T13:42:45.000Z","uid":40662,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35319f066974b7495b2427ebae6ed3f26a6b0974","tid":401323,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/--9BHKdBWetM/WbtaeV-bKfI/AAAAAAAAPnU/tsnZ9D-D_F0Xb514O23h8E0Wm1QHcieyQCLcBGAs/s1600/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F--9BHKdBWetM%2FWbtaeV-bKfI%2FAAAAAAAAPnU%2FtsnZ9D-D_F0Xb514O23h8E0Wm1QHcieyQCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&h=e68acdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11/9/2017 李克勤慶祝成立30週年演唱會（尾場）Rundown<br />\n<br />\n開Show時間：晚上八時三十分<br />\n完Show時間：晚上十一時五十九分<br />\n<br />\n01. 舊歡如夢<br />\n02. In The City<br />\n03. Medley：30克／紅日<br />\n04. 藍月亮<br />\n05. 當找到你<br />\n06. 告別校園時<br />\n07. 一生不變<br />\n08. 活著為求甚麼<br />\n09. 天水圍城<br />\n10. 二十四城記<br />\n11. 失魂記<br />\n12. 無朋友<br />\n13. 沒有你贏了世界又如何<br />\n14. 也曾相識（譚詠麟、李克勤合唱）<br />\n15. 一個人飛（譚詠麟獨唱）<br />\n16. 最愛<br />\n17. 左鄰右里<br />\n18. 今晚唱勁歌<br />\n19. 一枝花<br />\n20. 禮拜六無節目<br />\n21. 我著十號<br />\n22. 請你早睡早起<br />\n23. 閃電傳真機<br />\n24. 深深深<br />\n25. 偷偷摸摸<br />\n26. 不知不覺愛上你<br />\n27. 高妹<br />\n28. 情非首爾<br />\n29. 空中飛人<br />\n30. 眷戀<br />\n31. 妳是我的太陽<br />\n32. 希望<br />\n33. 夏日之神話<br />\n34. C3PO<br />\n35. 大會堂演奏廳<br />\n36. 命運符號<br />\n37. 一個都不能少<br />\n38. 球迷奇遇記<br />\n39. Victory<br />\n40. 護花使者<br />\n41. 回首<br />\n<br />\nEncore<br />\n42. 月半小夜曲<br />\n43. 舊生會<br />\n44. 合久必婚<br />\n45. 九月中的陌生人<br />\n46. 我不會唱歌<br />\n47. 一千零一夜<br />\n48. 再見穿梭機<br />\n49. 飛花<br />\n50. 紙牌屋<br />\n51. 只想您會意<br />\n52. 好戲之人<br />\n53. 誰願分手<br />\n54. 愛不釋手<br />\n<br />\n完整全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/09/HackenLee30th.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2FHackenLee30th.html&d=VDZ0rhTfcdrDQN359Iz3HaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=978b9e13\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/09/HackenLee30th.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae5b40dc84c32abc72c3b4334177a527722ca0e0","tid":401323,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"Overrun咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efb01e554976ea351c629f70beacc7d426ac27c","tid":401323,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Overrun咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n30mins"},{"pid":"d50afa3230a3bedc1931754cfa4b5742b29b05b6","tid":401323,"uid":44138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"今晚唱勁歌<br />\n一枝花<br />\n不知不覺愛上你<br />\n<br />\n睇得出佢真係有將tvb 做過既野放上心"},{"pid":"5008a2e3080846e23edac6af11770799753e62f4","tid":401323,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚唱勁歌<br />\n一枝花<br />\n不知不覺愛上你<br />\n<br />\n睇得出佢真係有將tvb 做過既野放上心</blockquote><br />\n但冇將啲die hard fans放上心呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滄海遺珠演唱會大大話話都講咗好多年！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37edf73a36ffc8e9760c07a69d2b1b3a87519756","tid":401323,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今晚唱勁歌<br />\n一枝花<br />\n不知不覺愛上你<br />\n<br />\n睇得出佢真係有將tvb 做過既野放上心</blockquote><br />\n但冇將啲die hard fans放上心呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滄海遺珠演唱會大大話話都講咗好多年！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得個講字<br />\n又想開又要驚好似95年咁"},{"pid":"7c9ee7889ab8488fad21c26c3976d64e1449d5c9","tid":401323,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><